{"tid":401073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓導彈發射成功  南韓導彈升空數秒墜海","createTime":"2017-09-15T10:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T12:24:19.000Z","uid":141461,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6ac1bdddc3b52c6e47ba1c52fdcaffd9c0ee56","tid":401073,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/160314_1bdd216f6fc0ccb4cc0d6bf266dd6b45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F160314_1bdd216f6fc0ccb4cc0d6bf266dd6b45.jpg&h=a176ac3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國聯合參謀本部（聯參）15日表示，鑑於朝鮮試射導彈。當地時間早上7點零3分，韓軍向朝鮮半島東部海域發射2枚「玄武-2A」彈道導彈，導彈升空僅數秒後即墜向海面。而朝鮮試射導彈成功橫過日本上空，墜落日本以東2000公里太平洋海域。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170915/_2017091511471463913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170915%2F_2017091511471463913.jpg&h=6c7f789d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據韓國紐西斯通訊社15日報道，聯參稱，目前相關機構正在調查導彈發射失敗的原因。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，這次韓軍發射的「玄武-2A」彈道導彈是射程在300公里以上的地對地彈道導彈。此外韓軍還裝備有「玄武-2B」（射程500公里以上）和「玄武-2C」（射程800公里以上）彈道導彈。"},{"pid":"6dcef3f3a5233807a7c103abf2f2654b9a06c385","tid":401073,"uid":52215,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:30:33.000Z","msg":"南韓柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n架佬又柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cd22f0f7e6139649fc0a7c9d84bebd2383cb2a","tid":401073,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"南韓 同 台灣 都真係東亞兩柒國"},{"pid":"8d74ba82efd2cdc806318cd8849a5df4478e0cd0","tid":401073,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170915/_2017091511471463913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170915%2F_2017091511471463913.jpg&h=1d3f2fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打到去阿留申群島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4bf2d7b8739b50b260c6233a6d7c60dce9fd60","tid":401073,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南韓柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n架佬又柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好柒點打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603dfa947e21b2fccc152dff7e55d70087756d39","tid":401073,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4cece08e35da9e931923dc1b65119709bd1982","tid":401073,"uid":48408,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:26:36.000Z","msg":"北泡支野竟然射遠過南泡咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cf2d9f12c45c5e679ce6c4b810d315d7b98cbb","tid":401073,"uid":2373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"之前覺得金仔好煩，之但係依家睇住佢當美日韓3國狗咁撚又好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f11b0fbe0130f82f044ea06e8d40c3d7a654c6","tid":401073,"uid":5394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2282/2282441.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.co